{
  "stem": "893.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He sort of arranged with their, with a friend of his who, who had a building, who owned a building in the ghetto, that just before they, they will be taken away from the ghetto, that they'll go into hiding with my mother and, and father and my brother and sister.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened is that the chief of the Gestapo, who was maybe a captain in the SS, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] got sick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe he needed an appendectomy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't trust the Hungarian doctors, military doctors, and the military hospital in our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted to have the, the operation performed in a private hospital through a private doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for that, he would have had to pay money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he ordered my father to be arrested and to be brought to his bedside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he came to him, he told him he needs 2,000 pengos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the Hungarian currency.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked him to go out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was still some Jewish doctors who were allowed to live outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some Jewish, baptized Jews who were baptized many, many years ago [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and were allowed to live outside, who were wealthy, and to raise the $2,000, 2,000 pengos and to bring it to him.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At one point in time, my father and mother, so did my father tell me, they decided that my father should go, even if she'll go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She will go into hiding, and my father should join us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- they were concerned about our well-being, and we might not survive on our own.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
